{"tid":1350482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果依一刻仲有撐警既屋企人或者父母, 覺得市民抵打","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T00:56:16.000Z","uid":125079,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37210e9b4b1b7c6a7b704a7ac44aefedfce890ac","tid":1350482,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"佢地已經係聽唔明人話<br />\n<br />\n完全唔識分析事情 冇人性 冷血<br />\n<br />\n依單野已經唔係黑警同示威者之間既事, 係直接打傷埋無辜市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有能力既盡快搬走, 唔好再同佢地一絲交流,  然後等佢地自生自滅</span>, 因為佢地已經唔算係人, 根本聽唔明人話 <br />\n<br />\n咁既情況都仲唔清醒, 我唔知道仲有啲咩事會令佢地醒覺<br />\n<br />\n冇能力走既, 忍到有能力走個日, 或者唔好再交流依啲野, 因為<span style=\"color: red;\">畜牲真係聽唔明人話</span>, 唔好再曬時間同心機<br />\n<br />\n只係激到自己想死"},{"pid":"60e4abb6e5279285509ffbe8a031e69078c9546b","tid":1350482,"uid":125079,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"推 祝福每一個人都有開明既父母 親戚"},{"pid":"533e6932cd421365b936d1eda8970fbaf1f684cf","tid":1350482,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"38568b2584873bb5dfe243adc32aaa949471909a","tid":1350482,"uid":4293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"由612開始已經發現冇得救<br />\n唔出聲算"},{"pid":"13a470c44cb8ab8b206b7843c195d93935bbbedf","tid":1350482,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"818f715335e0def40c049a8bd5add2c6ba539a3a","tid":1350482,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbna